00, and 16:00 UTC using a time-weighted average price mechanism. The funding payment occurs between long and short position holders based on the rate's sign and magnitude. MEXC's funding rate formula incorporates both interest rate differentials and premium components, with rates typically ranging from -0.75% to +0.75% per funding period for FLOKI pairs."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
